ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 160 - (Alberta) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 160 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of ALBERTA with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING in the watersheds of the Battle, Bow, Milk, Oldman, Red Deer and South Saskatchewan rivers from March 13 to April 15, 2011, inclusive.
